People kill for food.

00:16:56.110 --> 00:16:57.990
Parents sell their children.

00:16:57.990 --> 00:16:59.990
Children sell opium.

00:16:59.990 --> 00:17:01.780
Girls marry old men.

00:17:01.780 --> 00:17:05.730
Teenagers take responsibilities
that are too big.

00:17:05.730 --> 00:17:10.160
They feel old, begin to be
cruel, see things they shouldn't,

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:12.330
do things they shouldn't.

00:17:12.330 --> 00:17:14.050
You see women killed.

00:17:14.050 --> 00:17:17.030
Of course, they have
been raped first,

00:17:17.030 --> 00:17:19.650
because they are honored
by their enemies.

00:17:19.650 --> 00:17:23.400
And yes, you see yourself
used as a tool of war,

00:17:23.400 --> 00:17:27.740
and sold because no
one can protect you.

00:17:27.740 --> 00:17:31.960
War makes the warlord
thirstier and thirstier.

00:17:31.960 --> 00:17:36.020
He cares only about himself,
seeks to drink power,

00:17:36.020 --> 00:17:39.140
becomes blind, deaf, a liar.

00:17:39.140 --> 00:17:42.680
With no laws, no rules,
you make no goals anymore

00:17:42.680 --> 00:17:44.700
for your unknown future.

00:17:44.700 --> 00:17:47.240
You become cheap, worthless.

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:51.080
War means nightmares for
you, your family, your world.

00:17:51.080 --> 00:17:54.350
Every single sound scares you.

00:17:54.350 --> 00:17:57.100
War tastes as terrible as it is.

00:17:57.100 --> 00:18:02.340
You have no appetite, not
even for your favorite meal.

