because of my religion.

00:19:10.120 --> 00:19:14.340
No! God is not against love.

00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:17.380
He loves the one who is in love.

00:19:17.380 --> 00:19:18.700
I am in love.

00:19:18.700 --> 00:19:23.690
Yes! I am a girl and I am in love.

00:19:23.690 --> 00:19:26.980
Let me love the one who I want.

00:19:26.980 --> 00:19:30.430
Let me choose the one who I love.

00:19:30.430 --> 00:19:34.040
Let me experience what love is.

00:19:34.040 --> 00:19:38.240
Let me have something
that I want for myself.

00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:41.540
Men can fall in love
but women cannot.

00:19:41.540 --> 00:19:46.260
Why? We do not have a heart?

00:19:46.260 --> 00:19:48.340
We don't have feelings.

00:19:48.340 --> 00:19:50.350
We do not have choice.

00:19:50.350 --> 00:19:53.960
We are not human.

00:19:53.960 --> 00:19:55.320
Love is pure.

00:19:55.320 --> 00:19:57.620
Love is holy.

00:19:57.620 --> 00:19:59.580
Love is valuable.

00:19:59.580 --> 00:20:02.110
It is not against the law.

00:20:02.110 --> 00:20:04.570
It is not against religion.

00:20:04.570 --> 00:20:06.740
It is not against culture.

00:20:06.740 --> 00:20:08.940
It is not against humanity.

00:20:08.940 --> 00:20:15.060
